## 8. Variables de Entorno (Produccion)

| Variable | Descripcion | Ejemplo |
|----------|-------------|---------|
| `ASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT` | Entorno de ejecucion | `Production` |
| `ASPNETCORE_URLS` | URLs de escucha | `https://+:443;http://+:80` |
| `ConnectionStrings__DefaultConnection` | Cadena de conexion BD | `Server=...` |

```powershell
# Windows — configurar variable de entorno
$env:ASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT = "Production"
$env:ConnectionStrings__DefaultConnection = "Server=...;Database={{ db_name }};..."
dotnet {{ project_name }}.API.dll
```

